<div class=WordSection1 style='layout-grid:15.6pt'>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center;line-height:32.0pt'><b><span
style='font-size:22.0pt;font-family:宋体'>主持人讲话</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:21.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:18.0pt'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>各位领导、各位来宾，上午好！</span></p>

<p class=MsoBodyTextIndent style='line-height:18.0pt'><span style='font-family:
宋体'>首先感谢大家参加今天的开标会议。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:29.0pt;line-height:21.0pt'><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;letter-spacing:.25pt'>受</span><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>${twoBuyerName!}<span style='letter-spacing:
.25pt'>的委托，中国化工装备总公司对其所属</span><span lang=EN-US> <span
lang=EN-US style='color:windowtext;text-decoration:none'><span lang=EN-US>${buyerName!}</span></span> </span>
${bidProjectName}采购进行国内招标（招标编号：<span lang=EN-US>${bidProjectCode}</span>）。根据招标文件，本项目的投标截止时间已到，按照《中华人民共和国招标投标法》的规定，我们将拒绝接受此后递交的投标文件。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:28.5pt;line-height:18.0pt'><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>现在开标仪式开始。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:28.5pt;line-height:18.0pt'><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>首先，请允许我向大家介绍参加今天开标会议的领导和嘉宾。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:22.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;letter-spacing:.25pt'>1</span><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;letter-spacing:.25pt'>、</span><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>${twoBuyerName!}<u><span lang=EN-US
style='letter-spacing:.25pt'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></u><span lang=EN-US style='letter-spacing:.25pt'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:22.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;letter-spacing:.25pt'>2</span><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;letter-spacing:.25pt'>、</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'> <span
lang=EN-US style='color:windowtext;text-decoration:none'><span lang=EN-US>${buyerName!}</span></span> </span><u><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;letter-spacing:.25pt'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></u></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:26.95pt;line-height:18.0pt'><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;letter-spacing:.25pt'>今天共有<u> ${bidNum!}</u>家投标人参加开标。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:43.5pt;line-height:18.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;letter-spacing:.25pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:18.0pt'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>下面进行</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:18.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:18.0pt'><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>第一项：</span></b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>请<u><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></u><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;</span>讲话；</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:28.5pt;line-height:18.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>请 <u><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></u><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;</span>讲话；</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:18.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:18.0pt'><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>第二项：请投标人代表检查投标文件的密封情况。</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:18.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:18.0pt'><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>第三项：</span></b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>宣布唱标顺序、唱标内容和唱标的注意事项</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:56.25pt;text-indent:-20.25pt;line-height:
18.0pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>1．<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp; </span></span><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>唱标顺序为投标人递交投标文件的顺序；</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:56.25pt;text-indent:-20.25pt;line-height:
18.0pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>2．<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp; </span></span><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>唱标内容为：</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:18.0pt'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>投标人名称；投标报价；交货期；有无投标保证金；修改、撤消声明或附加说明；</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:36.0pt;line-height:18.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>3</span><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>．开标过程中允许录音、录像、拍照、记录；</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:18.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>唱标过程中允许投标人对误唱、漏唱的内容以即时举手或其他方式提出置疑。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:18.0pt'><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>第四项：介绍负责本次开标的工作人员</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:18.0pt'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>唱标人：<u><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></u>记录人：<u><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></u>监标人：<span
style='letter-spacing:.25pt'>${twoBuyerName!}监事处<u><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></u></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:36.0pt;line-height:18.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>下面唱标开始：<span lang=EN-US>**********************************************</span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:28.0pt;line-height:18.0pt'><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>各位投标人对唱标内容是否有疑义，如有疑义，请提出更正。如无疑义 ， 请唱标人、记录人、监标人及投标人在开标记录上签字。<span
lang=EN-US> </span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:7.0pt;line-height:18.0pt'><b><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>&nbsp;</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:18.0pt'><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>第五项：监标人宣读监标词</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:7.0pt;line-height:18.0pt'><b><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>&nbsp;</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:18.0pt'><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>第六项：宣布评标原则和定标办法。</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:7.0pt;line-height:18.0pt'><b><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>招标文件已有详细说明，为节省时间，这里不再重复。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:18.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:18.0pt'><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>第七项：宣布下一步工作、时间安排。</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:18.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>1</span><span style='font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>、开标后立即进入评标阶段，评委对投标文件初步审查和详细审查确定中标候选人，报招标人确定中标人。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:28.0pt;line-height:18.0pt'><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>经过评委审查后如果需要，则向投标人询标，请投标人保持通讯畅通，以便及时联系，询标不是对每个投标人都进行。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:14.0pt;text-indent:-14.0pt;line-height:
18.0pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>2</span><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>、开标后，或者请投标人询标后，投标人可以返回。中标方接到中标通知书后，按照要求，到<span
style='letter-spacing:.25pt'> <u><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></u></span>签订货合同。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:18.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>3</span><span style='font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>、投标单位的投标保证金按招标文件有关规定执行。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:18.0pt'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>&nbsp;</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:18.0pt'><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>第八项：注意事项</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:28.0pt;line-height:18.0pt'><a name=注意事项><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>今天开标大会结束后<span lang=EN-US>,</span>本项目的招标工作立即转入评标阶段。现将有关注意事项宣布如下，望大家遵照执行。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:18.0pt'><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>一、开标至评标结束，不允许投标商和评委工作人员私下接触。否则，可能导致其投标被拒绝。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:18.0pt'><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>二、评委及工作人员对评标工作必须保密，对投标文件的澄清和评标，将由评委会组织进行。评标澄清询问期间，不允许评委及工作人员向投标商私自透露评标的有关情况，也不允许评委与投标商进行私下接触。一旦发现，将按有关规定对其追究责任。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:18.0pt'><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>三、各投标厂商应按评委会的要求，及时向评委会进行必要的口头说明和提供必要的补充文件。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:18.0pt'><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>四、投标文件的澄清安排：</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:18.0pt'><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>各投标商的具体澄清时间和澄清内容，将另行通知。请各投标商在接到通知后，派技术人员和商务人员按时参加澄清会。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:18.0pt'><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>各位投标人，在其后将要开始的评标中，我们将按照《中华人民共和国招标投标法》的要求和本项目的特点，组建本项目的评标委员会。按照招标文件确定的评标标准和方法，对投标文件进行评审，本着“公平、公正、科学、择优”的原则，对待每一个投标人。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:18.0pt'><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>预祝各位投标人在本次投标中取得成功！</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:18.0pt'><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>开标仪式结束。谢谢大家。散会！ </span></p>

